To add to Chrome from source, follow the standard instructions for loading unpacked extensions:
1. Load Chrome's extensions page
2. Pop into Developer Mode
3. Select the 'Load unpacked extension...' option
4. Point it to the checkout directory.

Tested on Mac OSX 10.6, Ubuntu 10.04 with Chrome 8.x

